      "role": "user",
      "content": "i need to know if there's any way to explain what i'm feeling. i've been noticing this weird thing lately where when people lie to me, their voice literally feels like it's vibrating at a different frequency. like it's out of tune or hitting this specific sharp note that's just... wrong. is that even a real thing or am i just losing it?",
